Package: padctl
Version: 0.1.0
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: padctl maintainers <maintainers@padctl.dev>
Depends: systemd, bash
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/BANANASJIM/padctl
Description: HID gamepad remapper with declarative TOML config
 padctl is a HID gamepad compatibility daemon. It reads declarative
 TOML profiles and re-maps gamepad input via uinput, with per-device
 systemd socket activation and udev integration.
 .
 This package contains the prebuilt musl static binary.
